Project Is Based On Spring Boot Framework.
I have disabled spring boot security.
DataBase used is PostGreSql.

How to run :
  1. Please Install postgresql
  2. Update application.properties file as per your connection string

Post:
Url : http://localhost:8080/products/1
Request Body : 
{

        "name": "Kindal",
        "currentValue": {
            "price": 22233.23,
            "currencyCode": "USD"
        }
}

Get:
Url : http://localhost:8080/products/1
Response Body : 
{
        "id": 1,
        "name": "Kindal",
        "currentValue": {
            "price": 22233.23,
            "currencyCode": "USD"
        }
}
